            <thetext>The QxTarget.removeEventListener() method expects three arguments. The third argument however should be optional, for removing events that are not bound to a specific object.
Currently one must now, that for eventlisteners added to an object without a specific context object, an empty string is assumed to be given as third argument when the eventlistener is to be removed.

See thread on mailing list: http://www.nabble.com/removing-an-event-listener-t1756133.html</thetext>
